’Ů@78518b64f6ac9b2b134309f0adbf6959cc57d94447b31f292246292f39b93f7cÚTitle: title: date to-timezone
Path: Examples
Content:
Get the current date in UTC+05:00.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> date now | date to-timezone '+0500'


```
Get the current date in the local time zone.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> date now | date to-timezone local


```
Get the current date in Hawaii.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> date now | date to-timezone US/Hawaii


```
Get a date in a different time zone, from a string.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> "2020-10-10 10:00:00 +02:00" | date to-timezone "+0500"
Sat, 10 Oct 2020 13:00:00 +0500 (5 years ago)

```
Get a date in a different time zone, from a datetime.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> "2020-10-10 10:00:00 +02:00" | into datetime | date to-timezone "+0500"
Sat, 10 Oct 2020 13:00:00 +0500 (5 years ago)

```
’Ů@2d6d4436199c05a82dd9fd055d90e8820aaba7ff83a7388886f366966314d1ccŮoTitle: title: date to-timezone
Path: Notes
Content:
Use 'date list-timezone' to list all supported time zones.
